_sText:
ScubazScoutzKnifez

Really fun map when a lot of ppl play on it.

Includes:

Scout Vending Machines

Two big buildings on each side of the lake, two floors.
Ladders in back go onto the roof.
Ladders inside go to 2nd floor w/ windows

Inside the building are vending machines, incase you run out of ammo, just press the button and out comes a scout.

Roof has lots of cover to take out your foes.
2nd floor has windows
1st floor has a strafe wide open window, just jump onto the stairs and start sniping.

In the middle of the water is a fully loaded awp (use your knife to jump across to the platform)

Have Fun!!! :)
